fill in questions in the init_db.sql file up to you, categories as many as you want with 4 possible answers on each question


docker-compose down
docker-compose up --build

# Remove the volume of DB if needed
docker volume rm quizlet_postgres_data


Quizlet is here:
http://localhost:3000





